videos.description: Cincinnati's Gary Clark scores with an easy two-handed dunk off the pass from Cane Broome.
videos.headline: Clark flushes for the Bearcats

videos.description: Cleveland State's Tyree Appleby drives the lane and scores on a right-handed layup.
videos.headline: Appleby scores a sweet finger roll layup

videos.description: Tre Scott knifes through the Cleveland State defense and hops up for a slam dunk.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Scott hop, skip and jumps for dunk

videos.description: Trevor Moore hits a buzzer-beating 3-pointer at the half for the Bearcats.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Moore sings the nylon song at the buzzer

videos.description: Gary Clark slams home an alley-oop dunk off the feed from Justin Jenifer to extend the lead for the Bearcats.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Jenifer, Clark combine for fast-break alley-oop dunk

videos.description: The Bearcats swing the ball around and finds an open Justin Jenifer who nails an open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's great ball movement leads to open 3-pointer

videos.description: Kyle Washington outmuscles three Cleveland State defenders, gains the ball and scores on a right-handed shot for an old-fashioned three-point play.
videos.headline: Washington's strong take leads to 3-point play
